Senior Electrical Engineer
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 16:01:10
Ref. JB3046372
Job Description
- Electrical Estimation during tender stage.
- Design Electrical systems.
- Monitor and control expenses related to the electrical works and ensure organizational forecasts and budgets will meet these expenses.
- Evaluating subcontractor offers against the specifications scope of work.
- Review and evaluate technical submittals and shop drawings prior to submission to consultants and clients according to required project specifications.
- Quantity take off and review contracts monthly invoices.
- Prepare the Pr and PO for electrical materials as per the drawings and specifications.
Skills
- Minimum 10 years of experience.
- Very good oral and written communication, motivated, problem solving, social, diplomatic.
- Quality / result driven on time.
- Conversant of CAD 2D and 3D / REVIT.
- Strong knowledge with ASTM
Education
Bachelor of Electrical Engineering
